snippet.title: New Player Guide to Retail World of Warcraft | TWW Season 2 Ep. 13
snippet.description:
In this episode! Yogrt does more timewalking... and some crafting!.

We also cover a variety of endgame gearing concepts and topics including:
- How to get weapons and armor crafted in retail world of warcraft
- We finish the undermine campaign to earn an Enchanted Runed Undermine Crest
- What happens when a season changes, what currency goes away
- Enchanting your gear
- Adding sockets and gems to your gear
- Tertiary stats
- And more!

snippet.title: World of Warcraft | Ödland | #13 (No Commentary Gameplay)
snippet.description:
Willkommen zu einem No-Commentary-Gameplay von World of Warcraft Retail, das die ikonischen Zonen von Azeroth feiert. Ich erkunde die Welt von Azeroth, wie sie sein sollte: lebendig, detailreich und voller Nostalgie. Von spannenden Quests bis zu den atemberaubenden Landschaften – dieses Gameplay lädt dich ein, die Magie der Welt in aller Ruhe zu erleben. Ob du vertraute Pfade beim Leveling neu entdeckst oder einfach die Stimmung von WoW genießen möchtest, dieses Video ist für dich. Lehne dich zurück und tauche in die Welt der Quests und Abenteuer ein. 

Weitere Videos dieser Art findest du in der Playlist:

https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLJW4fojtQCp6lQBLnsISjdbyiieV8_81I

Welcome to Undermine—the shadowy, gold-laced underworld where greed meets danger and Treasure Goblins don’t go down without a fight! 🪙💥 In this fast-paced hunt through the twisting tunnels of The War Within, we chase down elusive goblins in search of rare loot, big gold, and maybe a surprise or two… 🎁⚒️

UWoW крупный русскоязычный проект с несколькими серверами на разных версиях. Самый большой сервер Legion икс 100 насчитывает порядка четырех - пяти тысяч онлайн. Хардкорный мир Legion икс три насчитывает примерно тысячу но на нем более свежий контент. Кроме того, есть еще новый мир Legion Plus! Сервер открылся 2 января и в настоящий момент имеет около трех тысяч онлайн. Особенности мира заключаются в том, что начиная с десятого уровня, качаться можно в любой локации, любого дополнения. CD рейдов сбрасываются каждый день, добавлены новые эпохальные подземелья из Warlords of Draenor и что самое интересное, расширен функционал хардкора. Во время прокачки вы не только получаете новые хардкорные таланты, но и само испытание становится сложнее, от уровня к уровню. Если вам нравится Hardcore, попробовать определенно стоит!

snippet.title: World of Warcraft : Revisiting Azeroth - Session 20
snippet.description:
Session 20 in Retail World of Warcraft, playing a human Paladin, Alexplorer.

The start of the journey will be to redo all the original Vanilla zones in their current retail format, with the plan to lock my XP gain when I hit level 35 until I complete Wrath of the Lich King.

I am also planning to limit myself to mostly Classic items (except storage and cosmetics) until I have completed all the Classic quests and areas. I will not be using Heirlooms or food or buffs from later expansions intentionally, but I am also not planning to stress about it too much.

Then after I have done these stories, I will move through to World of Warcraft expansions.

Occasionally I might revisit my other more powerful characters, either for support, or just to learn something.


World of Warcraft by Blizzard Games
https://worldofwarcraft.blizzard.com/en-us/

#WorldofWarcraft #WoW

snippet.title: World of Warcraft : Revisiting Azeroth - Session 19
snippet.description:
Session 19 in Retail World of Warcraft, playing a human Paladin, Alexplorer.

The start of the journey will be to redo all the original Vanilla zones in their current retail format, with the plan to lock my XP gain when I hit level 35 until I complete Wrath of the Lich King.

I am also planning to limit myself to mostly Classic items (except storage and cosmetics) until I have completed all the Classic quests and areas. I will not be using Heirlooms or food or buffs from later expansions intentionally, but I am also not planning to stress about it too much.

Then after I have done these stories, I will move through to World of Warcraft expansions.

Occasionally I might revisit my other more powerful characters, either for support, or just to learn something.


World of Warcraft by Blizzard Games
https://worldofwarcraft.blizzard.com/en-us/

#WorldofWarcraft #WoW
